text: Survivor Series (2013) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on November 24, 2013 at the TD Garden in Boston, Massachusetts. It was the twenty seventh Survivor Series event held by WWE. In the main event, Randy Orton defeat Big Show to keep his WWE Championship. In other matches, John Cena defeated Alberto Del Rio to keep his World Heavyweight Championship, and CM Punk and Daniel Bryan defeated The Wyatt Family's Luke Harper and Erick Rowan. ==Matches== === Survivor Series elimination matches === Eliminated Wrestler Eliminated by Method Time Dean Ambrose Cody Rhodes Pinfall 02:13 Jack Swagger Jey Uso 08:13 Antonio Cesaro Cody Rhodes 09:58 Jimmy Uso Roman Reigns 14:33 Cody Rhodes 15:43 Jey Uso Seth Rollins 16:47 Seth Rollins Rey Mysterio 19:43 Goldust Roman Reigns 22:58 Rey Mysterio 23:23 Roman Reigns (Team Shield & Real Americans) Eliminated Wrestler Eliminated by Method Time Alicia Fox Naomi Pinfall 01:24 Cameron Rosa Mendes 02:28 Rosa Mendes Nikki Bella 02:45 Summer Rae 03:27 Eva Marie Kaitlyn 04:01 Naomi 04:34 Kaitlyn Brie Bella 05:12 Brie Bella Aksana 05:42 Aksana Nikki Bella 06:04 JoJo AJ Lee 09:28 Tamina Natalya Submission 10:51 AJ Lee 11:29 Natalya and Nikki Bella (Total Divas) ==References== ==Other websites== *Official Survivor Series 2013 website Category:2013 in American television Category:2013 in professional wrestling Category:Sports in Boston Category:Survivor Series Category:2013 in Boston Category:November 2013 events
